Several server updates:
1: Bulk update. Add network now adds data, attributes, nodes and links in bulk, providing
significant performance increases. A more generic solution has yet to be developed.
2: Image upload. Added an add_image, get_image and remove_image handler. The location of
the images is set in config. (this has yet to be tested on windows)
3: XML. Three XSDs have been specified at a basic level to represent the network / node / link layout
strings, the plugin input format and the plugin output format. These have yet to be tested.
4: Several tests have been updated in line with changes to the server.
5: An index has been added to tResourceAttr to speeed up query times.
